Package: TRexSelectorNeo
Type: Package
Title: T-Rex Selector: High-Dimensional Variable Selection & FDR Control
Version: 0.2.0
Description: FDR-controlled variable selection for regression and classification in
 high-dimensional settings while controlling the false discovery rate (FDR) at a user-specified
 target level. The R package comes as R bindings to the TRexSelector C++ library and
 supersedes the pure-R 'TRexSelector' package, alongside which it can be installed.
